  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 158 to define \"organization\" as a federally recognized patriotic civic service organization that consists of or serves youths; permit an organization to request and require superintendents to provide an opportunity to provide information to students on school property during a school day."
